cs.DC, cs.LG, cs.AR, cs.NA, cs.CE 

The paper discusses benchmarking of data analysis and machine learning applications on the Intel KNL many-core processor. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also focuses on the performance of machine learning applications, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the architecture and design of the KNL processor, which could place it in cs.AR (Architecture). The use of benchmarks and performance metrics suggests that it could also belong to cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). Finally, the paper discusses the practical applications of the KNL processor, which could place it in cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
